1527776999-srandom_entropy_onehour.mp4.title: Random Number Generator From /dev/srandom
1527776999-srandom_entropy_onehour.mp4.description:
The Source ::::: https://github.com/josenk/srandom
The Code ::::: shuf --random-source=/dev/srandom -r -i 1-100000000 | while read -r line; do convert -gravity center -depth 8 -size 768x576 -pointsize 75 -font /usr/share/fonts/truetype/cmu/cmunrm.ttf label:$line yuv:-; done | x264 --input-res 768x576 -o srandom_entropy_onehour.mp4 --fps 10 --frames 100000 -

1527777366-srandom_entropy_onehour_color.title: Random Color Generator From /dev/srandom
1527777366-srandom_entropy_onehour_color.description:
The Source ::::: https://github.com/josenk/srandom
The Code ::::: shuf --random-source=/dev/srandom -r -i 0-16777215 | while read -r line; do r=$(expr $line \/ 65536);g=$(expr \( $line \/ 256 \) \% 256 );b=$(expr $line \% 256); convert -gravity center -depth 8 -size 768x576 -background "rgb($r,$g,$b)" -pointsize 75 -font /usr/share/fonts/truetype/cmu/cmunrm.ttf -stroke black -fill white "label:rgb($r,$g,$b)" yuv:-; done | x264 --input-res 768x576 -o srandom_entropy_onehour_color.mp4 --fps 10 --frames 100000 -
